<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA621_07_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema621_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_07_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">
          <div class="fraction_row">
            <div class="fraction_inn">
              바닷물
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span class="whole f32b">4</span>
                <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>2</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              g을 페트리 접시 한 개에
              <span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
              씩 나누어 담으려고 합니다. 필요한 페트리 접시는 몇 개인지 구해 봅시다.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_07_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="input_area">
                  <h3 lang="y">구하는 식을 써 보세요.</h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="4(1)/(2)-:(3)/(4)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_07_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="input_area">
                  <h3 lang="y">
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span class="whole f32b">4</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                        <span>1</span>
                        <span>2</span>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                    &divide;
                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
                    을 어떻게 계산할 수 있을지 이야기해<br>보세요.
                  </h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                          <p>대분수를 가분수로 바꾼 다음 통분하여 계산하거나 분수의 곱셈<br>으로 나타내어 계산할 수 있습니다.</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
              <h3 lang="y">
                대분수를 가분수로 바꾼 다음 하윤이와 재민이의 방법으로 계산해 보세요.
              </h3>
              
              <div class="question_box">
                  <div class="col1">
                    <p class="nm">하윤</p>
                    <div class="bubble_txt">
                      통분하여<br>계산해 볼까?
                    </div>
                    <div class="col1_inn">
                      <span class="mixed_fraction f32b">
                        <span class="whole">4</span>
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                          <span>1</span>
                          <span>4</span>
                        </span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
                      <span class="f32b">=</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                        <span class="input_wrap ipt1">
                          <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
                        </span>
                        <span>2</span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
                      <span class="f32b">=</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                        <span class="input_wrap ipt1">
                          <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="18"></math-field>
                        </span>
                        <span class="f32b">4</span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                        <span class="input_wrap ipt1">
                          <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                        </span>
                        <span>4</span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">=</span>
                      <span class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="18"></math-field>
                      </span> 
                      <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
                      <span class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                      </span> 
                      <span class="f32b">=</span>
                      <span class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                      </span> 
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col2">
                    <p class="nm">재민</p>
                    <div class="bubble_txt">
                      분수의 곱셈으로<br>나타내어<br>계산해 볼까?
                    </div>
                    <div class="col1_inn">
                      <span class="mixed_fraction f32b">
                        <span class="whole">4</span>
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                          <span>1</span>
                          <span>4</span>
                        </span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
                      <span class="f32b">=</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                        <span class="input_wrap ipt1">
                          <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
                        </span>
                        <span>2</span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
                      <span class="f32b">=</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                        <span>9</span>
                        <span>2</span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">&times;</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                        <span class="input_wrap ipt1">
                          <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                        </span>
                        <span class="input_wrap ipt1">
                          <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                        </span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="f32b">=</span>
                      <span class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                      </span> 
                    </div>
                  </div>
                   
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_4">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_07_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="input_area">
                  <h3 lang="y">필요한 페트리 접시는 몇 개인가요?</h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span class="f32b">개</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_5">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_07_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="input_area">
                  <h3 lang="y">(대분수)&divide;(진분수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                          <p>대분수를 가분수로 바꾼 다음 통분하여 계산하거나 분수의 곱셈<br>으로 나타내어 계산합니다.</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
